          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The waters saw You, O God; The waters saw You, they were in anguish; The deeps also trembled. "
